  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Don't tick him off!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Exploding Vengeance]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/7d2bbcefac13cd379c1c08638c718626.poster.avif?t=1770900324\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/7d2bbcefac13cd379c1c08638c718626.webm?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/7d2bbcefac13cd379c1c08638c718626.mp4?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kevin, the retired war hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having lost everything to the alien invaders,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >he was reborn from the brink of death as a cyborg of fury!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, his explosive revenge drama begins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Ultra-Fast Run & Gun Action]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/e058824ff1722172b47a67cbdac24ee6.poster.avif?t=1770900324\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/e058824ff1722172b47a67cbdac24ee6.webm?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/e058824ff1722172b47a67cbdac24ee6.mp4?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relentless speed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dazzling effects covering the screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powerful impact and thrilling feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience ultra-fast combat that awakens all your senses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Complete Your Style with Combat Suits]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/ad693574dbee6ee8df87f4da50358a26.poster.avif?t=1770900324\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/ad693574dbee6ee8df87f4da50358a26.webm?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/ad693574dbee6ee8df87f4da50358a26.mp4?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire various suits during combat and use them strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each suit awaits with unique looks and destructive abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete your own combat style and seize victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Perfect Harmony of Precision Controls, Puzzles & Action]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/f020276cbf9dffd4da682745b168a680.poster.avif?t=1770900324\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/f020276cbf9dffd4da682745b168a680.webm?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/f020276cbf9dffd4da682745b168a680.mp4?t=1770900324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even amidst ultra-fast combat, split-second decisions determine fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision jumps, controls testing your reflexes,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and witty puzzles that don't break the flow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the thrilling action that stimulates both hands and mind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Vast Helios System Exploration]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093800/extras/867d28396596733bcdccb310e2fa0151.avif?t=1770900324\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Across 9 planets, 5 moons, and 10 chapters,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unearth hidden collectibles and mysteries,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and fight against unpredictable, powerful bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Key Features]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 Breathtaking Ultra-Fast Action</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡 Unique & Powerful Combat Suits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 Vast Planets & In-Depth Exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👑 Overwhelming Epic Boss Battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ Exhilarating Revenge of the Hero Turned Cyborg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[A World Built Together]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feedback shapes our future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the conversation on our Discord, X,</p>",
